  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time media search across movies, TV shows, and people",
    "Hybrid watchlist with local-first storage and cloud sync via Convex",
    "Granular episode tracking with progress calculation",
    "Multiple watch statuses and emotional reactions",
    "Secure authentication with Clerk",
    "Optimistic UI updates with TanStack Query",
